  "obverse": {
    "description": "Large crowned and armored portrait of King Christian IV over a line. Shield with arms of Denmark below the line. King's portrait is within a beaded line cut below by the shield. Legend is outside the circle, along the rim. King's motto is within the circle along the border.\r\nKing's hair falls over the collar. There are 9 Hearts in Denmark arms",
