  "reverse": {
    "description": "Female figure, representing Fortuna, is standing tall on a small globe. Her body is partially covered by a shawl and have a curved position with head facing left. She also helds a long flying banner with right hand above head, keeping it at hip size with the left. Fortuna is partially within a beaded circle with legend outside. Date and mintmark are at end of legend",
